<h2 id="usage">Usage</h2>
<p>Cards are native web components usable through the <code>&lt;tcds-card&gt;</code> custom element. The <code>image</code>, <code>title</code>, <code>link</code>, and <code>description</code> slots are provided to insert respective content into the Card body (see examples).</p>
