<h3 id="responsive-orientation">Responsive orientation</h3>
<p>The Card&#39;s orientation is vertical (image above content) by default, but will become horizontal (image to the left of content) if its parent container is wider than 600px.</p>
<p>If you wish to change the Card&#39;s default orientation before responsive calculations are made, you can set the <code>orientation</code> attribute to <code>horizontal</code>.</p>
<p>You can also lock the Card into a particular orientation by adding <code>lock</code> to the <code>orientation</code> attribute value.</p>

