<h2 id="implementation">Implementation</h2>
<h3 id="progressive-enhancement">Progressive enhancement</h3>
<p>If the JavaScript fails to execute and register the custom element that creates the card, the content will still be accessible as a plain image floated to the left of plain text. This will be the result in browsers that do not support the JavaScript techniques used to program the component, as well as clients that fail to load the required assets.</p>
